# Prisma migrations live here.
#
# - Created by:    pnpm --filter @domera/api db:migrate:dev --name <desc>
# - Applied by:    pnpm --filter @domera/api db:migrate:deploy
# - Inspect with:  pnpm --filter @domera/api db:migrate:status
#
# Do NOT manually edit applied migrations — create a new one instead.
# Raw SQL that Prisma can't express (partial unique, RLS, policies) either
# lives inside `migration.sql` of a Prisma migration, or in a standalone raw
# SQL file under prisma/migrations-sql/ / prisma/rls/.
